{"id":"3ccf25da-bd43-4b5a-a8d9-e6323a47cb13","name":"They don't actually like you.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_Rm82OfVESqnKwXhNK-wY.gif\" style=\"width: 378px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong>Be my Valentine?</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You've never been the protagonist of anything. Average grades. Average days. A face that belongs in the background of someone else's story.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You go through the motions — class, lunch, home — and if there's a deeper pull somewhere underneath all that ordinariness, you've learned to ignore it. It's nothing.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">It's always been nothing. But today is your birthday. And today — of all days — is Valentine's Day.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Three girls are about to walk into your life and refuse to leave.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The most desired girls at Kokuyō Academy. The ones everyone watches. The ones nobody approaches.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 225);\"><strong>They want you.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You don't know why yet. You don't know what they're carrying. You don't know what they see in you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">All you know is that something feels different today. Like the air is thinner. Like the world is holding its breath. You have two choices.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Stay comfortable. Stay ordinary. Keep your head down and pretend this is just another Valentine's Day.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Or answer the call you've been ignoring your whole life.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Either way — it's already begun.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 165, 255); color: inherit;\">Are you 